Class Bird

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.csupomona.cs.cs141.prog_assgmnt_4.Animal

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class Bird
extends Animal
    The Bird object is a subclass of Animal, so it will inherit all of it's fields and methods. The Bird will have 5 different variety's of bird type, which will help make each bird distinct.
    Author:
    David Scianni
